data.description: 3 Bedroom, 2 full bath that sits on a nice quiet country side setting on just over an acre! The living room, dining room and kitchen are all open with a cathedral ceiling. The main bedroom with walk in closet and private bath ensuite are on one side and the other end of the home offers 2 bedrooms and a full bath. This is a great opportunity for the new buyer(s) to use their creativity with all the perks of the big ticket items already completed! In 2023:  the sellers added insulation to the exterior and then all new siding, a new driveway was installed, a new manhole cover was placed on the septic and the front deck was installed. In 2022: water heater was replaced, approx. 3 yrs ago the well pressure tank was replaced, approx. 5 yrs. ago the HVAC system was replaced, and approx. 10-15 yrs ago a 30 yr. architectural shingle roof and new Anderson windows were installed. There is an underground propane tank which the sellers purchased and own and the house is being sold with all appliances including the whole house generator. There's even a a large chain linked fenced-in area in the backyard. The house and inclusions are all being sold AS-IS & is priced accordingly.  The only thing it needs is the creative cosmetic ideas, elbow grease and a little love to design your new home! Inspections are welcome but are for buyers knowledge only.
